# Profile flow

Read **docs/contracts/flow-profile.md** before changing profile, scorecard, or player modal preview.

## Required patterns

1. Profile mutations via services — not direct Supabase in components.
2. Player modal must not leak private fields to non-host viewers.
3. Sign out flows through `AuthContext` so pending deep links and realtime teardown stay consistent.

